<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>🌟 Welcome Home</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #89f7fe, #66a6ff);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 50px 35px;
      max-width: 850px;
      width: 100%;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
      animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3em;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #ffeb3b;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      color: #f5f5f5;
    }

    .section {
      margin-top: 35px;
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-size: 1.9em;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: #ffe082;
    }

    .emoji {
      font-size: 2em;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 28px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6a00, #ee0979);
      color: white;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1.1em;
      transition: transform 0.2s, background 0.3s;
    }

    a:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ee0979, #ff6a00);
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      font-size: 0.95em;
      color: #eee;
    }

    /* Animation */
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <h1>🏡 Home Sweet Home!</h1>
    <p>Welcome to our little corner of the web 😊</p>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>🌈 What You’ll Find Here</h2>
      <p>🚀 Fast performance<br>
         🧠 Smart ideas<br>
         🎨 Beautiful design<br>
         🤝 Friendly community</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>📅 Today's Mood</h2>
      <p class="emoji">😎🔥💡🍀💻</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>👣 Take the Next Step</h2>
      <a href="/about">Learn About Us →</a>
    </div>

    <footer>
      <p>🌟 Made with love | © 2025</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
